List all connected devices

Usage: wheelctl device list [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -d, --detailed             Show detailed device information
      --json                 Output in JSON format for machine parsing
      --hid-observe-only     List only observe-only HID endpoints, without service/mock devices
  -v, --verbose...           Verbose logging
      --json-out <JSON_OUT>  Write the device list receipt to this JSON file
  -h, --help                 Print help
